 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Front-End Development Engineers Sky Republic Scottsdale, AZ Position Charter 
 We are looking for highly talented and motivated engineers to join our R&D team, expand the capabilities of our innovative blockchain platform Atlas, and build applications for our customers. 
 Atlas eliminates supply chain fragmentation due to point to point EDI or API through next-generation smart contracts. It automates community processes and data reconciliation among participants without disrupting business models or infrastructure. 
 Atlas was built from the ground up for Fortune 2000s and blockchain consortia to easily track assets, certify provenance, accelerate payments and settlements, and enable new IoT/Artificial Intelligence/Mobile solutions. 
 Atlas offers the best features of Ethereum, Fabric, Corda, and middleware to power Digital Supply Chain. 
 Candidates must be interested in solving problems that have never been solved before, drive product components development from design to production. 
 
 Role and Responsibilities 
 Drive the end-to-end design and implementation of feature-rich React components for the core Atlas platform and its applications. 
 Contribute to a highly creative and experienced team in an agile and collaborative environment to release new UIs for Atlas. 
 Continuously learn and bring-in industry practices and technology for web design and web development. 
 Apply software development best practices such as unit testing, code review, test automation and continuous delivery to produce high quality software. 
 Work with various stakeholders and customers to develop the Sky Republic offering and ensure its adoption. 
 Participate in all phases of development including design, coding, deployment, testing, documentation and maintenance of Sky Republic solution. 
 
 
