 Desire and ability to rapidly learn new technologies, put them in practice with tough deadlines, and work through challenging problems. 
 In-depth understanding of JavaScript, HTML, CSS, the DOM, and relevant concepts 
 Experience testing JavaScript single-page applications (using Jest, Mocha, Enzyme, etc.) 
 Familiar with Linux container technologies (Docker, CoreOS) and associated stack (Docker swarm, Kubernetes etc.) 
 Proficient with agile (Scrum/Kanban/XP) software development methodology and continuous delivery techniques and tools (Jenkins, Git, Jira etc.) 
 Possess strong interpersonal, leadership, and communication skill 
 Able to work in a very fluid environment with a high degree of autonomy 
 
 Bonus Qualifications 
 Familiar with the concepts behind modern Blockchain technologies (Hyperledger, Corda, Ethereum) 
